lf on a success. Emptying a vial of holy water on the target also ends the effect on it."},{title:"Stunning Screech",content:"The vrock emits a horrific screech. Each creature within 20 feet of it that can hear it and that isn't a demon must succeed on a DC 14 Constitution saving throw or be stunned until the end of the vrock's next turn ."}]}]}